Class ChiselUIPage

java.lang.Object
com.Ev0sMods.Ev0sChisel.ui.ChiselUIPage
public final class ChiselUIPage extends Object
Unified Chisel UI – combines in-world block chiselling and inventory-based table conversion into a single page with two switchable modes.
  • Chisel mode – click a variant to replace the targeted block in the world.
  • Table mode – select a block from inventory, then convert it into chisel variants (left-click = all, right-click = half).
